        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">.display-6 — Alternative</div>
          <div class="display-6" style="margin: 0;">Découvrir</div>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-size-9 • 40px • Weight: 700</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
{% endset %}

{% set body_content %}
  <div class="typography-demo">
    <section class="typography-section">
      <div class="typography-demo__grid">
        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">.lead — Lead paragraph</div>
          <p class="lead" style="margin: 0;">Situé au cœur du 8ème arrondissement de Paris, cet appartement d'exception offre une vue imprenable sur les Champs-Élysées. Avec ses 180 m² parfaitement agencés, ce bien prestigieux saura séduire les clients les plus exigeants.</p>
          <div class="demo-alphabet" style="margin-top: var(--size-3); font-size: 1.125rem;">
            ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br>abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br>1234567890(,.;:?!$&*)
          </div>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-size-2 • 18px • Line-height: 1.625 (relaxed)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">&lt;p&gt; — Body paragraph (default)</div>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Ce magnifique appartement de 4 pièces dispose d'un double séjour lumineux, de trois chambres spacieuses, de deux salles de bains modernes et d'une cuisine équipée haut de gamme. Les prestations comprennent le parquet massif, les moulures d'époque, une cheminée en marbre et une cave.</p>
          <div class="demo-alphabet" style="margin-top: var(--size-3);">
            ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br>abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br>1234567890(,.;:?!$&*)
          </div>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-size-1 • 16px • Line-height: 1.5 (normal)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">&lt;small&gt; — Small text</div>
          <p><small style="margin: 0;">Charges mensuelles : 450€ • Taxe foncière : 2 800€/an • Copropriété de 12 lots • DPE : C (110 kWh/m²/an) • GES : B (8 kg CO2/m²/an) • Honoraires à la charge du vendeur.</small></p>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-size-0 • 14px • Usage: Captions, legal text</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">.micro — Micro text</div>
          <p class="micro" style="margin: 0;">Réf. 2024-PAR-8-001 • Publié le 15/11/2024 • Dernière mise à jour : 08/12/2024 à 14:32</p>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-size--1 • 12px • Usage: Metadata, timestamps</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
{% endset %}

{% set styling_content %}
  <div class="typography-demo">
    <section class="typography-section">
      <h3>Font Weights</h3>
      <div class="typography-demo__grid">
        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">Light (300)</div>
          <p style="font-weight: var(--font-weight-300); margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Un immeuble haussmannien de prestige</p>
          <div class="demo-alphabet" style="margin-top: var(--size-3); font-weight: 300;">
            ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br>abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br>1234567890(,.;:?!$&*)
          </div>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-weight-300 • Usage: Subtle emphasis (rare)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">Regular (400)</div>
          <p style="font-weight: var(--font-weight-400); margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Un immeuble haussmannien de prestige</p>
          <div class="demo-alphabet" style="margin-top: var(--size-3); font-weight: 400;">
            ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br>abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br>1234567890(,.;:?!$&*)
          </div>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-weight-400 • Usage: Body text (default)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">Bold (700)</div>
          <p style="font-weight: var(--font-weight-700); margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Un immeuble haussmannien de prestige</p>
          <div class="demo-alphabet" style="margin-top: var(--size-3); font-weight: 700;">
            ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br>abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br>1234567890(,.;:?!$&*)
          </div>
          <small class="demo-notes">Token: --font-weight-700 • Usage: Headings, strong emphasis</small>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin-top: var(--size-12);">Line Heights (Leading)</h3>
      <div class="typography-demo__grid">
        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">--leading-tight (1.25)</div>
          <p style="line-height: var(--leading-tight); margin: 0;">Cet appartement d'exception offre des prestations haut de gamme dans un cadre architectural remarquable. Les volumes généreux et la luminosité naturelle créent une atmosphère unique.</p>
          <small class="demo-notes">Usage: Headings h1–h3</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">--leading-normal (1.5)</div>
          <p style="line-height: var(--leading-normal); margin: 0;">Cet appartement d'exception offre des prestations haut de gamme dans un cadre architectural remarquable. Les volumes généreux et la luminosité naturelle créent une atmosphère unique.</p>
          <small class="demo-notes">Usage: Body text (default)</small>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-demo__item">
          <div class="demo-code">--leading-relaxed (1.625)</div>
          <p style="line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin: 0;">Cet appartement d'exception offre des prestations haut de gamme dans un cadre architectural remarquable. Les volumes généreux et la luminosité naturelle créent une atmosphère unique.</p>
          <small class="demo-notes">Usage: Lead paragraphs, long-form content</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
{% endset %}

{% include '../_base-story.twig' with {
  header: header,
  sections: [
    {
      title: 'Typography Scale Overview',
      description: 'Complete reference table of all typography tokens, sizes, and their intended usage across the design system.',
      badge: 'Quick Reference',
      content: overview_content
    },
    {
      title: 'Heading Elements',
      description: 'Semantic heading elements (h1–h6) form the document structure with responsive sizing. Always prefer semantic markup for accessibility and SEO.',
      badge: 'Semantic Elements',
      content: headings_content
    },
    {
      title: 'Display Classes',
      description: 'Non-semantic display classes (.display-1 to .display-6) for large, impactful text in hero sections and campaigns. Use sparingly when semantic markup isn\'t possible.',
      badge: 'Display Utilities',
      content: display_content
    },
    {
      title: 'Body Text',
      description: 'Reading text styles for content hierarchy. Lead paragraphs introduce sections, body text for main content, small text for captions, and micro text for metadata.',
      badge: 'Reading Text',
      content: body_content
    },
    {
      title: 'Text Styling',
      description: 'Font weights and line heights to control text emphasis and readability. Combine these utilities with size tokens for precise typography control.',
      badge: 'Utilities',
      content: styling_content
    }
  ]
} only %}
